abstract: Tunisian authorities round up group of people suspected to be  militants returning from Syria and Iraq three days after fatal bus attack claimed by Islamic State.
lead_paragraph: The authorities arrested 40 people and put 92 others under house arrest on suspicion that they were militants returning from Syria and Iraq.

headline.main: Tunisia: Terrorism Suspects Held After Raids
